    "headline": "Meta Targets $9 Trillion Value With Exec Pay Plan. It’s Bolder Than Musk’s Tesla Package.",
    "summary": "Meta Platforms  has unveiled ambitious executive pay incentives, targeting a $9 trillion market capitalization by 2031 as it looks to get ahead in the intensifying AI talent race.  Under the stock options program, which includes six leaders but not CEO Mark Zuckerberg, the full value of the options would only be realized if Meta stock jumps more than 500% to $3,727, according to filings late Tuesday.  Meta stock rose 0.9% ahead of the open Wednesday.",
